 and\nnon-isomorphic models: which we believe the literature on dualities has not so\nfar discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Jul 2017 19:11:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Jan 2018 11:55:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-04"}
