dered. However, for one of the\nmodels, the constraint on the coupling parameter does not improve the present\nresult (achieved using a large combination of surveys), and a larger\ncombination of probes appears to be necessary to eventually claim whether or\nnot interaction is favored in that context.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Jul 2017 10:28:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Oct 2017 10:24:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 22 Nov 2017 14:59:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-23"}
